data.title: Princess Märtha of Sweden, Queen Maud of Norway and Olav, Crown Prince of Norway, later Olav V
data.meta_description: Photograph of a full length group portrait of, from left to right, Princess Märtha of Sweden, Queen Maud of Norway and Olav, Crown Prince of Norway, later Olav V. The group  are posed on top of a small flight of stairs and face the camera front on. Queen Maud is seated at the centre of the photograph and Princess Märtha and Prince Olav stand either side of her. The group are dressed for the Coronation of King George VI. Queen Maud wears a ermine  cloak with a long train....
